Package model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CassetteCollection
    CassetteCollection extends MusicCollection and outlines the basic variables needed for a Cassette collection.
    CDCollection
    CDCollection extends MusicCollection and outlines basic variables needed for a CD Collection Artist: The name of the artist of the CD.
    DVDCollection
    DVDCollection extends MoviesCollection and outlines basic variables needed for a DVDCollection.
    LaserDiscCollection
    LaserDiscCollection is an extension of MoviesCollection and outlines the basic variables needed for a LaserDisc Collection.
    MoviesCollection
    MoviesCollection is a parent class to DVD, LasesrDisc, and VHS.
    MTGCollection
    MTGCollection extends TCGCollection and outlines the basic variables needed for a Magic to Gathering Collection.
    MusicCollection
    MusicCollection is a parent class to Cassette, CD, and Vinyl.
    PokemonCardCollection
    PokemonCardCollection extends TCGCollection and outlines basic variables needed for a Pokemon Card Collection.
    Storage
    The storage class is responsible for temporary storage of the collections when reading and writing to their respective files.
    TCGCollection
    TCGCollection (Trading Card Game) is the parent class for PokemonCardCollection, YuGiOhCollection, and MTGCollection.
    VHSCollection
    VHSCollection is an extension of MoviesCollection and outlines the basic variables needed for a VHS Collection.
    VinylCollection
    VinylCollection is an extension of MusicCollection and outlines the basic variables needed for a Vinyl Collection.
    YuGiOhCollection
    YuGiohCollection extends TCGCollection and outlines basic variables needed for a YuGiOh Card Collection.
